          <h4>Property</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-13">
          <p>Laurel oil content (prevents redness and irritation)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Use</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-18">
          <ul>
            <li>Daily care</li>
            <li>Hydration</li>
            <li>Active hydro-liquid protection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-item table-head" id="block-4">
          <h4>Aleppo Soap 35% Laurel oil</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Your Skin Type</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-9">
          <p>Sensitive and allergic skin</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Property</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-14">
          <p>For very sensitive, irritated skin.</p>
          <p>
            Suitable for people suffering from more serious skin problems such as     
          psoriasis or eczema.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Use</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-19">
          <ul>
            <li>Daily care</li>
            <li>Hydration</li>
            <li>Active hydro-liquid protection</li>
            <li>Soothes problem skin</li>
            <li>Actively soothes dry skin problems</li>
            <li>Restores the pH of the epidermis</li>
            <li>Anti stubborn dandruff</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-item table-head" id="block-5">
          <h4>Aleppo Soap 40% & 55% Laurel oil</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Your Skin Type</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-10">
          <p>Hyper sensitive skin</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Property</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-15">
          <p>For hyper sensitive, irritated skin.</p>
          <p>
            With its high percentage of 40% bay laurel oil, our soap is designed     
          to provide optimal hydration and nourishment, making it suitable for
          hypersensitive skin, suffering from acne, eczema, psoriasis, scabs,
          dry skin, dandruff.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-label secondary">
          <h4>Use</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item col-value" id="block-20">
          <ul>
            <li>Daily care</li>
            <li>Hydration</li>
            <li>Active hydro-liquid protection</li>
            <li>Soothes problem skin</li>
            <li>Actively soothes dry skin problems</li>
            <li>Restores the pH of the epidermis</li>
            <li>Anti stubborn dandruff</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "t:sections.main-page.name",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "section",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "t:sections.all.padding.section_padding_heading"
      },
      {
        "type": "color",
        "id": "background_colour",
        "label": "Background Colour",
        "default": "transparent"
      },
      {
        "type": "image_picker",
        "id": "image",
        "label": "Banner Image"
      },
      {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "padding_top",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 100,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "t:sections.all.padding.padding_top",
        "default": 36
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "padding_bottom",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 100,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "t:sections.all.padding.padding_bottom",
        "default": 36
      }
    ]
  }
{% endschema %}